    "• Post-processing.",
    "Post-processing methods start from the LLMs output text and process it again to remove bias.",
    "It involves rewriting the output or swapping harmful keywords for semantically similar words with more positive connotations (Gallegos et al., 2023).",
    "• Self-correction.",
    "Ganguli et al. (2023) showed that models can leverage themselves to correct their biases."
